data.description: Welcome to this spacious and versatile ranch-style home nestled in the desirable & unrestricted Maywood Acres neighborhood. With 2,639 square feet of well-designed living space on a sprawling 1.2 acres, this prop. offers a unique opportunity for comfortable multi-generational living or rental income potential.The main residence features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, providing ample space for a family or guests. Add., a separate private casita with 1 bedroom & 2 baths offers flexible living arrangements for extended family or as a rental unit. This home has been thoughtfully updated, boasting modern upgrades in the kitchen, bathrooms, & all the flooring. It's a place where neighbors become friends, & the tranquility of rural living meets the convenience of being just minutes away from major transportation routes. Easy access to Highway 59/69, 99, and 242, this home makes commuting a breeze. Schedule a viewing of this unique prop. today; your dream home with dual living quarters awaits!
